<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1437,153,971]" pageId="9" pageNumber="443">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,909,935]" pageId="9" pageNumber="443">Etymology.</emphasis>
The species is named on the basis of the Greek word “ 
<emphasis box="[962,1060,910,935]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="443">megistos</emphasis>
”, which refers to the large discal spots on both two wings.
</paragraph>
